channel.title: Error_game_js5connect help [718]
channel.description:
Okay let me explain this,
I have my server up and running and I do have players playing on it as we speak but all of a sudden I tried to start up my client and it wont load. stays at 0% then I get this error. "error_game_js5connect"
Yes the client connected to the server perfectly fine earlier today, yes I checked the port and ip, it's correct. Yes the server is online. Not sure why it's doing it and I thought I'd ask on here so I can stop wondering about this. lol. Thanks

item.title: Error_game_js5connect help [718]
item.dc:creator: @pure2ownage Pure_
item.description:

[quote=“Jolley, post:3, topic:540407”][quote author=Pure_ link=topic=659264.msg4409049#msg4409049 date=1392936141]
You changed something, perhaps use version control to roll back your changes (or go through them by last modified date).
[/quote]

I’m not sure what I changed… I’m so confused. I didn’t change nothing because the client was perfectly working fine connecting to my server a few hours ago…[/quote]Your firewall/router might have decided to block the connection? Double check them and make sure you are absolutely positive you changed nothing.
